<p>Go for it! While they weren't perfectly in sync both ladies gave it their all</p>

<p>Leah revealed her daughter Kier, 12, was behind the camera in her caption, adding: 'Also I think Kiki is a future film maker' with a laughing with tears emoji.</p>

<p>The girls got plenty of attention with the post.</p>

<p>Castmate Sonja Morgan had a question, taking to the comments to wonder: 'How do you that gurl? I’m actually on the way to the chiropractor. Literally. Now and watching this.'</p>

<p>The ousted RHONY castmate returned to the comment section later to say: 'Teach me for Ramona’s next party.'  </p>

